{
  "name": "XPath",
  "summary": "<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/XPath/XPath .htm#XPath.SetValue\">SetValue</a></strong> 方法可将 XPath 映射到区域或列表列。<strong>SetValue</strong> 方法也用于更改现有 XPath 的属性。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/XPath/XPath .htm#XPath.Clear\">Clear</a></strong> 方法可删除已映射到区域或列表列的 XPath。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例基于被附加到活动工作簿的“catalog_映射”架构映射，在活动工作表上创建了一个 XML 列表，然后使用SetValue方法将每个列绑定到XPath对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Specify the schema map to use.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xmlMap = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">XmlMaps</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;catalog_映射&quot;</span>)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Create a new list.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>()\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Specify the first element to map.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xPath1 = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;/catalog/book/@id&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Map the element.</span>\n    listObject.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ListColumns</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">XPath</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetValue</span>(xmlMap, xPath1)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Specify the second element to map.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xPath2 = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;/catalog/book/author&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Add a column to the list.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listColumn1 = listObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListColumns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Map the element.</span>\n    listColumn1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">XPath</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetValue</span>(xmlMap, xPath2)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xPath3 = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;/catalog/book/title&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listColumn2 = listObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListColumns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>()\n    listColumn2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">XPath</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetValue</span>(xmlMap, xPath3)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果映射到工作表 Sheet2 上单元格E3的XPath被映射到XML列表，则显示该XPath值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xPath = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">XPath</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (xPath.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Repeating</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(xPath.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表已被映射到 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a></strong> 或 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ListColumn/ListColumn .htm#ListColumn.ListColumn\">ListColumn</a></strong> 对象的 XPath。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Map",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/XmlMap/XmlMap .htm#XmlMap.XmlMap\">XmlMap</a></strong> 对象，该对象表示包含指定 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/XPath/XPath .htm#XPath.XPath\">XPath</a></strong> 对象的架构映射。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示包含活动工作表上单元格B1的XPath架构映射的XmlMap的第一个XML架构的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xPath = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">XPath</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(xPath.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Map</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Schemas</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示包含第一张工作表上单元格B2的XPath架构映射的XmlMap关联绑定的SourceUrl属性值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xPath = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">XPath</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(xPath.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Map</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataBinding</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SourceUrl</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "XmlMap",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Repeating",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果指定的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/XPath/XPath .htm#XPath.XPath\">XPath</a></strong> 对象被映射到 XML 列表，则返回 <strong>True</strong>；如果 <strong>XPath</strong> 对象被映射到单个的单元格，则返回 <strong>False</strong>。<strong>Boolean</strong> 类型，只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示映射到第一张工作表上单元格C2的XPath是否被映射到XML列表。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xPath = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">XPath</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(xPath.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Repeating</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果映射到活动工作表上单元格A2的XPath被映射到XML列表，则清除该XPath架构信息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xPath = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">XPath</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (xPath.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Repeating</span>) {\n        xPath.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Clear</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Value",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>String</strong>，它代表指定对象的 XPath。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示映射到A1单元格的XPath的值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">XPath</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将映射到活动工作表上D1单元格的XPath的值赋值到A7单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xPath = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">XPath</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A7&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = xPath.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Clear",
      "summary": "<p><strong>Clear</strong> 将影响映射到 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/XPath/XPath .htm#XPath.XPath\">XPath</a></strong> 对象的整个区域。</p>\n<p>此方法不从映射到指定 XPath 的单元格中清除数据。使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Clear\">Clear</a></strong> 方法可从单元格中清除数据。</p>\n<p>如果指定的 XPath 在 XML 列表中被映射，则将删除架构映射，但列表不会从工作表中删除。</p>\n<p>如果映射的区域是单个单元格，则将删除这个单元格，但会保留数据。</p>\n<p>如果满足以下任一条件，此方法将生成错误：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>区域跨网格中的多个列。</li>\n<li>区域的某个部分包含已经映射的单元格，剩余部分包含未映射的单元格。</li>\n<li>区域的某一部分包含一个映射，而另一部分包含了不同映射或同一映射中的不同 XPath。</li>\n</ul>\n",
      "description": "<p>清除映射区域的所有 XPath 架构信息。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例清除映射到单元格B1的所有XPath架构信息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">XPath</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Clear</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果映射到活动工作表上单元格C1的XPath值字符串的长度大于0，则清除该XPath架构信息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xPath = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">XPath</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (xPath.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">length</span> &gt; <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>) {\n        xPath.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Clear</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "SetValue",
      "summary": "<p>有关 ET 中 XPath 支持的说明，请参阅 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/XmlMap/XmlMap .htm#XmlMap.IsExportable\">IsExportable</a></strong> 属性。如果 XPath 表达式无效或者已经映射了指定的 XPath，则将发生运行时错误。</p>\n<p>如果 ET 无法解析命名空间，则将发生运行时错误。</p>\n<p>如果满足以下任一条件，此方法将生成错误：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>区域跨网格中的多个列。</li>\n<li>区域的某个部分包含已经映射的单元格，剩余部分包含未映射的单元格。</li>\n<li>区域的某一部分包含一个映射，而另一部分包含了不同映射或同一映射中的不同 XPath。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>如果区域是单一单元格，则 ET 在默认情况下创建不重复的单一映射单元格。此不重复单元格无标题。</p>\n<p>当单一单元格区域位于 ListObject 中时，会出现例外；这时映射信息应用于整个列。</p>\n<p>如果区域包含多个单元格，ET 将创建一个重复的 XML 列表。ET 将选定区域作为所有数据值进行处理；因此，在创建 XML 列表后，该区域将下移一行，并且标题位于该区域顶部占用的单元格中。插入行位于移动后的区域的底部。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>对象模型中不使用 ET 的标题检测算法。这里假设网格中不存在标题。</li>\n<li>在对象模型中创建映射区域时，将禁用自动合并和自动扩大。</li>\n</ul>\n",
      "description": "<p>将指定的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/XPath/XPath .htm#XPath.XPath\">XPath</a></strong> 对象映射到 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基��接口/表格 API 参考/ListColumn/ListColumn .htm#ListColumn.ListColumn\">ListColumn</a></strong> 对象或 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a></strong> 集合。如果 <strong>XPath</strong> 对象先前已被映射到 <strong>ListColumn</strong> 对象或 <strong>Range</strong> 集合，则 <strong>SetValue</strong> 方法将设置 <strong>XPath</strong> 对象的属性。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例基于被附加到活动工作簿的“catalog_映射”架构映射，在活动工作表上创建了一个 XML 列表，然后使用SetValue方法将每个列绑定到XPath对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Specify the schema map to use.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xmlMap = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">XmlMaps</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;catalog_映射&quot;</span>)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Create a new list.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>()\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Specify the first element to map.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xPath1 = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;/catalog/book/@id&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Map the element.</span>\n    listObject.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ListColumns</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">XPath</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetValue</span>(xmlMap, xPath1)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Specify the second element to map.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xPath2 = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;/catalog/book/author&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Add a column to the list.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listColumn1 = listObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListColumns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Map the element.</span>\n    listColumn1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">XPath</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetValue</span>(xmlMap, xPath2)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xPath3 = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;/catalog/book/title&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listColumn2 = listObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListColumns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>()\n    listColumn2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">XPath</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetValue</span>(xmlMap, xPath3)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例基于被附加到活动工作簿的“catalog_映射”架构映射，使用SetValue方法将工作表 Sheet2 上第一个列表的第一列绑定到XPath对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xmlMap = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlMaps</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;catalog_映射&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xPath = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;/catalog/book/@id&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> range = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ListColumns</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    range.<span class=\"hljs-property\">XPath</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetValue</span>(xmlMap, xPath, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ex&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Map",
          "type": "XmlMap",
          "description": "<p>将与映射区域相关联的映射信息。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        },
        {
          "name": "XPath",
          "type": "string",
          "description": "<p>一个有效的 XPath （XML 路径语言 (XPath)：用来获取部分 XML 文档的语言。XPath 也提供操作字符串、数字和布尔值的基本工具。）表达式，指示 ET 应在该映射区域中显示哪些 XML 数据。XPath 字符串可能还包含有效筛选；在这种情况下，该映射区域只会显示 XPath 指向的数据的子集。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        },
        {
          "name": "SelectionNamespace",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>指定用于 <em>XPath</em> 参数的任意命名空间 （命名空间：一种唯一限定元素名称与关系的方法，以避免具有同一名称但来自多个来源的元素发生名称冲突。）前缀。如果 <strong>XPath</strong> 对象不包含任何前缀，或者 <strong>XPath</strong> 对象使用了 ET 内部前缀，将省略该参数。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "Repeating",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>指定 <strong>XPath</strong> 对象是否绑定到 XML 列表的某一列，或是否映射到单个单元格。设置为 <strong>True</strong> 会将 <strong>XPath</strong> 对象绑定到 XML 列表的某一列。设置为 <strong>False</strong> 会强制创建不重复的单元格。如果区域大于单个单元格且指定了 <strong>False</strong>，则将发生运行时错误。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        }
      ],
      "returns": "void"
    }
  ]
}